<h4>User Login</h4>
<p>
As opposed to users logging in with their email address (which I found was extremely irritating) users are now able to login with their username.  This servers two purposes.  One is convenience, which was previously mentioned; and two, it gives the @replies the ability to function correctly without having to map to a user's email.  Users' emails are utilized for the sole purpose to link their Gravatars. <span class="label label-info">Modification</span>
</div>
