<h4>Gravatar</h4>
<p>
As stated before, if your email address is using a Gravatar,
Ampersand will automatically fetch your avatar and use it here on the site.  If you wish to have a Gravatar, simply go edit your profile and sign up for one.  (It takes two seconds) <span class="label label-success">Developed</span>
</p>
